{"tid":1032980,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返套漫畫","createTime":"2019-02-22T18:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T02:55:51.000Z","uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8333ef53ca06ec6291867ed1f0db6189e845bac3","tid":1032980,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:51:47.000Z","msg":"內容大約係咁<br />\n<br />\n一個學校保健室女老師 , 用d 特別既藥解決學生/老師既問題<br />\n<br />\n有一話係講個女仔想減肥, 呀老師就比左隻藥佢食然後叫佢千祈唔好食肉,<br />\n個女仔一開頭都ok, 直到阿哥要比賽之前一日屋企煮肉佢終於忍唔住,<br />\n最終就變左隻怪物比個老師殺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一話就係講一個訓導老師錯手殺死左個學生, 咁呀保健室老師又出手,<br />\n用訓導老師既健康黎換返個女學生既生命, 條件係一個星期內keep住食一隻藥,<br />\n同埋個人會變到好似BB咁無力, 巧合地遇上一次學生比不良少年既圍攻,<br />\n佢選擇見死不救, 後來比個學生撞返, 屌鳩佢平時成日係學校當d 學生垃圾,<br />\n將佢支藥丟鳩走左, 最後呀訓導老師就一邊行路一邊溶化死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係Google 搵左好耐都搵唔返, 套野好似係得兩期咁大把, 唔知有無巴打有睇過呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2abca5feb2971d6adcf6fabd6041a3a6e65e406","tid":1032980,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T19:45:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d5c7b72f9608cc91878067cac0adbf908773916","tid":1032980,"uid":27662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T21:14:55.000Z","msg":"學校怪談 危險女教師"},{"pid":"ec03124f5da5e7a71b2664e0ed5676521c4c53ed","tid":1032980,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d5c7b72f9608cc91878067cac0adbf908773916","tid":1032980,"uid":27662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T21:14:55.000Z","msg":"學校怪談 危險女教師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\"